featured.text: These bacteria are found in the nose and are easily 18 to the eye when you rub your nose, then your eye.

definition.zh_def: 鼻子，位於臉部的器官，用於嗅覺和呼吸。
definition.en_def: The organ on the face used for smelling and breathing.
definition.example: She wrinkled her nose at the unpleasant smell.
